# Haugen

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Jump to: navigation, search

**Haugen** is a Norwegian surname and place name frequently used for farm
homesteads. Haugen derives from the [old Norse](/wiki/Old_Norse "Old Norse")
word _haugr_ meaning tiny hill, small grassy knoll, or mound. Derivatives also
include the Norwegian surnames [Haugan](/wiki/Haugan_\(name\) "Haugan
\(name\)") and [Hauge](/wiki/Hauge_\(disambiguation\) "Hauge
\(disambiguation\)"). Haugen can refer to:
